## Spectrum of a ring
Let $R$ be a ring.<!-- .element: class="fragment" data-fragment-index="1" -->

$\operatorname{Spec} R = \\{ \text{ prime ideals } \mathfrak p \leq R  \\}$<!-- .element: class="fragment" data-fragment-index="2" -->

e.g. $\operatorname{Spec} \mathbb Z = \\{(0), (2), (3), (5) \ldots\\} $ <!-- .element: class="fragment" data-fragment-index="3" -->

